<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 40px; line-height: 1.6;">
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">Request for Bonafide Certificate</h3>

    <p style="text-align: right;">Date: {{date}}</p>

    <p>To,<br />
        The Principal/Registrar,<br />
        {{institutionName || "Your Institution"}}</p>

    <p>Subject: Request for issuance of Bonafide Certificate for Scholarship Purpose.</p>

    <p>Respected Sir/Madam,</p>

    <p>I am <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>, a student of <strong>{{courseName}}</strong> (Year {{yearOfStudy}}) in your
        esteemed institution. My UID/Roll Number is ____________________.</p>

    <p>I am applying for the <strong>{{scholarshipName || "Scholarship Portal"}}</strong> and require a Bonafide
        Certificate as mandatory documentation for the same. I request you to kindly issue the certificate at the
        earliest.</p>

    <p>Thanking you,</p>

    <div style="margin-top: 60px;">
        <p>Yours Sincerely,</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 40px;">__________________________</p>
        <p><strong>{{fullName}}</strong><br />
            Address: {{address}}<br />
            Ref: {{docId}}</p>
    </div>
</div>